headline: Show HN: List of Hacking Resources
description:
I have a list of hacking resources that I have recently been collecting, they include resources where you can learn hacking and tools to hack, most of it is for pentesting

Practical and tools https://www.youtube.com/c/PentesterAcademyTV/videos https://malwareunicorn.org/#/resources https://sectools.org/ https://start.me/p/EL84Km/cse-utopia https://start.me/p/b5Aow7/asint_collection https://start.me/p/rx6Qj8/nixintel-s-osint-resource-list https://start.me/p/wM7y15/search-engine https://start.me/search/google-startme?q=s https://github.com/moonD4rk/HackBrowserData https://hackaday.io/projects

Learning https://www.youtube.com/c/PentesterAcademyTV/videos https://tryhackme.com/room/tutorial https://malwareunicorn.org/#/workshops https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SFbV7sTSAlA&t=108s https://class.malware.re/ https://www.thehacker.recipes/ https://www.malwaretech.com/tag/tutorials https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-KBm3tBNK74&list=PLidcsTyj9JXL4Jv6u9qi8TcUgsNoKKHNn https://academy.hackthebox.com/ https://casvancooten.com/posts/ https://start.me/p/rx6Qj8/nixintel-s-osint-resource-list https://cryptohack.org/ https://hackaday.io/projects https://www.hacksplaining.com/lessons
